03:54.321 --> 03:55.844
[water running]

04:17.257 --> 04:19.694
[coughing]

04:21.957 --> 04:23.698
Pull yourself together.

04:38.060 --> 04:39.453
[door shuts]

04:58.863 --> 05:00.387
[knob rattles]

05:22.017 --> 05:23.627
[window tapping]

05:27.022 --> 05:28.545
Hello?

05:29.198 --> 05:31.331
I'm locked in.

05:33.855 --> 05:36.248
