05:37.815 --> 05:39.121
Hello?

05:47.564 --> 05:49.653
Hey, I'm locked in!

05:59.620 --> 06:02.753
[no dialogue]

06:07.367 --> 06:09.064
Hey!

06:09.107 --> 06:11.109
Hey, I'm locked in!

06:44.882 --> 06:48.103
[Robbie] Stay with me, forever.

06:50.018 --> 06:52.977
Hey! Can anyone hear me?

07:12.127 --> 07:13.345
Help!

07:13.389 --> 07:16.000
Hello, is anyone here?
I'm locked in!

07:16.044 --> 07:17.611
I can't get out!

07:19.569 --> 07:21.876
I can't get out, hello!

07:46.074 --> 07:48.859
- [panting]
- [lock rattling]

07:48.903 --> 07:50.644
[whimpering]

07:55.170 --> 07:57.477
Please, I'm locked in.

07:57.955 --> 07:59.130
Hello!

08:01.393 --> 08:03.918
[Robbie] Stay with me, forever.

08:05.833 --> 08:07.008
Robbie?

08:10.664 --> 08:13.928
Lana, stay with me.

08:14.711 --> 08:15.756
Forever.

08:25.592 --> 08:27.071
Lana...

08:33.730 --> 08:36.516
[screaming]

09:06.546 --> 09:07.938
Thanks, Colette!

09:17.078 --> 09:19.776
Hey, babe, what's up?

09:19.820 --> 09:22.518
Well, look who
decided to finally call.

09:22.562 --> 09:26.566
- [chuckles]
- So, Vincent Miller
left you a message.

09:26.609 --> 09:28.655
Remind me which one
that is again?

09:28.698 --> 09:30.265
Remember the Civil War
historian?

09:30.308 --> 09:31.832
We reached out to him
regarding his family's

09:31.875 --> 09:33.703
connection with
the Lincoln assassination?

09:33.747 --> 09:35.575
The one out of Long Island.

09:35.618 --> 09:38.403
Yup, he said
we can interview him.

09:38.447 --> 09:40.797
Here, take down his numberso you can give him a call back.

09:40.841 --> 09:42.190
Okay.

09:43.278 --> 09:44.888
- All right, ready?
- Go.

09:44.932 --> 09:49.719
516-555-1088.

09:51.460 --> 09:52.679
Got it?

09:53.723 --> 09:55.595
Oh, my God, this is great.

09:57.161 --> 09:58.380
All right, love you.

09:58.423 --> 10:00.164
Call him and let me know
what he says.

10:00.208 --> 10:01.862
You're the best, thanks so much.

10:01.905 --> 10:05.082
-All right, see you at home.
-Okay, bye babe, I love you.

10:06.606 --> 10:09.130
[alternative rock music]

10:11.567 --> 10:13.656
[whispers] Okay. Okay.

10:22.665 --> 10:24.536
[mellow rock music]

10:29.890 --> 10:32.327
[phone ringing]

10:40.727 --> 10:42.119
[Vincent] Hello.

10:43.730 --> 10:45.383
Well, hello to you.

10:47.516 --> 10:50.040
