10:50.084 --> 10:52.521
Of course my offer still stands.

10:52.564 --> 10:54.523
And we have plenty of rooms.

10:55.829 --> 10:57.961
We have plenty of rooms.

10:58.005 --> 11:00.268
How many of you are there?
Great.

11:00.311 --> 11:02.836
