11:58.369 --> 12:01.851
I'm just, uh,
taking photographs
of this influencer, whatever.

12:01.895 --> 12:03.940
What's up?

12:03.984 --> 12:06.377
So, I... I secured a cover

12:06.421 --> 12:08.249
for that gig
I was telling you about

