and it starts tomorrow,
and I thought...

12:12.644 --> 12:14.211
maybe you could bring your kit.

12:14.255 --> 12:17.171
Okay.
Well, what'd you find out?

12:18.694 --> 12:21.784
Nothing yet, but it's, uh...

12:21.828 --> 12:24.004
It's actually real near
where everything started.

12:24.047 --> 12:26.267
Wait, you actually mean...

12:26.310 --> 12:27.834
[man] Yeah.

12:27.877 --> 12:29.966
All roads lead back
to the funeral parlor.

12:30.010 --> 12:32.360
- [man grunts]
- [door creaks]

