I gotta tell Joey about this.

13:10.833 --> 13:13.880
- Hey...
- Shit, I have no
cell service down here.

13:15.751 --> 13:18.885
- Check this out.
- Oh, shit.

13:18.928 --> 13:20.321
You like that?

13:20.364 --> 13:23.150
I like it. [laughs]

13:28.155 --> 13:29.852
