13:29.896 --> 13:31.462
[banging]

13:31.506 --> 13:34.944
- You hear that?
- Let 'em watch.

13:34.988 --> 13:36.772
I thought
I heard something back there.

13:37.773 --> 13:40.950
No... Where are you going?

13:40.994 --> 13:43.474
- Frankie.
- Look, babe, I know
that you're an exhibitionist,

13:43.518 --> 13:45.433
but we're trespassing.

13:45.476 --> 13:47.348
- I'm just gonna close the door.- Okay.

13:47.391 --> 13:49.002
Be right back.

13:49.045 --> 13:51.482
- Go protect us.
