I live with many secrets,
Ms. Weingarten,
but one of them is this;

55:09.784 --> 55:12.700
It has bothered me
my entire life

55:12.744 --> 55:15.529
that the whole world
thinks that John Wilkes Booth

55:15.573 --> 55:19.751
was the mastermind
behind the assassination
of President Abraham Lincoln

55:19.794 --> 55:21.753
when it was my great-grandfather

55:21.796 --> 55:25.887
who was the sole mastermind
behind the killing.

55:26.497 --> 55:28.063
Oh.

55:28.760 --> 55:30.588
I see.

55:32.024 --> 55:35.332
Well, when did your
