56:16.111 --> 56:18.070
I have it.

56:18.113 --> 56:19.419
You have it.

56:19.463 --> 56:20.942
[laughs]

56:20.986 --> 56:22.596
Where?

56:23.510 --> 56:25.947
Like... here?

56:28.385 --> 56:29.560
Okay.

56:29.603 --> 56:32.693
So, uh, one last question:

