your story to tell?

56:35.479 --> 56:38.395
You're opening yourself
to Pandora's Box.

56:38.438 --> 56:41.223
Any nutjob will be
banging down your door.

56:41.267 --> 56:44.705
I live with Pandora's Box,
Ms. Weingarten.

56:45.314 --> 56:46.315
Let them come.

