to set the record straight

57:05.160 --> 57:11.166
and... talk about
who he actually was.

57:11.210 --> 57:13.952
Well, thank you.

57:13.995 --> 57:16.998
Thank you, Mr. Miller,
for telling me your story.

57:17.042 --> 57:18.478
My pleasure.

57:29.097 --> 57:30.534
