1:10:31.575 --> 1:10:32.793
[mutters]

1:10:32.837 --> 1:10:35.361
[Scratch]
Janet, what are you doing?

1:10:35.405 --> 1:10:36.623
[laughs]

1:10:41.846 --> 1:10:43.195
[water running]

1:10:43.239 --> 1:10:46.154
[Janet]
Oh, shit, there's no soap.

1:10:46.198 --> 1:10:50.071
Scratch, can you hand me
the soap, please?

1:10:50.115 --> 1:10:51.334
[giggles]

1:10:51.856 --> 1:10:53.901
Uh, yeah.

1:10:54.772 --> 1:10:55.947
Sure.

1:11:04.912 --> 1:11:07.828
Here, uh, look up
above the shower curtain.

1:11:07.872 --> 1:11:09.787
[Janet] I can't reach that.

1:11:09.830 --> 1:11:13.921
Can you hand it to me
like a gentleman, please?

1:11:14.400 --> 1:11:15.836
[giggles]

1:11:22.321 --> 1:11:23.714
There you go.

1:11:23.757 --> 1:11:25.368
Where's the soap?

1:11:25.411 --> 1:11:28.284
- Oh-oh here.
- [giggles]

1:11:29.241 --> 1:11:31.678
It's really hot in here.

1:11:31.722 --> 1:11:33.506
You don't like it steamy?

1:11:33.550 --> 1:11:34.855
[both giggle]

1:11:34.899 --> 1:11:38.250
Not when I can't see you,
that's no fun.

1:11:39.817 --> 1:11:42.820
I didn't think we'd
be doing this right here.

1:11:44.735 --> 1:11:46.302
I can't see you.

1:11:46.345 --> 1:11:47.999
I'm sure if you wanted

1:11:48.042 --> 1:11:51.524
you could reach out
and touch me.

1:11:52.438 --> 1:11:55.354
Janet, it's really hot in here.

1:11:56.877 --> 1:11:57.922
[growling]

1:11:57.965 --> 1:11:59.489
[yelling]

1:11:59.532 --> 1:12:01.534
[groaning]

1:12:39.964 --> 1:12:41.226
Hello!

1:12:49.408 --> 1:12:51.628
[laughing]

1:12:55.022 --> 1:12:56.546
Hello?

1:12:57.677 --> 1:12:59.418
[ears ringing]

1:12:59.462 --> 1:13:01.638
[panting]

1:13:05.468 --> 1:13:08.819
Hello, can you hear me?

1:13:21.658 --> 1:13:23.311
Hello?

1:13:23.355 --> 1:13:26.489
[Mrs. O'Brian] In here, sweetie.

1:13:27.925 --> 1:13:29.883
[child giggles]

1:13:32.712 --> 1:13:35.715
[Mrs. O'Brian]
Come on in, sweetie.

1:13:35.759 --> 1:13:39.719
Come on, come on!

1:13:39.763 --> 1:13:41.982
I'm waiting for you.

1:13:42.026 --> 1:13:44.420
It's me.

1:13:44.463 --> 1:13:49.076
It's me. [laughing]

1:13:54.125 --> 1:13:55.953
Hello?

1:13:55.996 --> 1:13:58.390
[Mrs. O'Brian]
Come in here, sweetie.

1:13:58.434 --> 1:13:59.696
[laughing]

1:14:00.871 --> 1:14:04.614
I can hear you.
[laughs]

1:14:04.657 --> 1:14:07.181
I can hear you.

1:14:07.225 --> 1:14:09.923
- [laughs]
- Mrs. O'Brian?

1:14:13.405 --> 1:14:14.711
[screaming]

1:14:14.754 --> 1:14:17.322
[laughing]

1:14:17.365 --> 1:14:19.455
[screaming]

1:14:26.636 --> 1:14:28.464
[choking]

1:14:32.729 --> 1:14:34.557
[crickets chirping]

1:14:39.953 --> 1:14:42.913
This is what
you're gonna do, McMahon.

1:14:42.956 --> 1:14:45.132
You're gonna clean up
my investment.

1:14:45.176 --> 1:14:47.831
You're gonna put it
in that machine, see.

1:14:47.874 --> 1:14:50.877
And you're gonna run production as planned.

1:14:53.184 --> 1:14:55.665
Do I make myself clear,
Mr. McMahon?

1:14:55.708 --> 1:14:59.277
Because... I won't hesitate.

1:14:59.320 --> 1:15:02.585
I will shoot you right here,
right now.

1:15:02.628 --> 1:15:04.717
Right where you stand.

1:15:04.761 --> 1:15:07.851
-Oh, God.
- Do I make myself clear?

1:15:07.894 --> 1:15:09.592
- Mr...
- I hate this show.

1:15:09.635 --> 1:15:12.638
[laughing]

1:15:16.599 --> 1:15:19.427
Nancy,
why do you like such crap?

1:15:19.471 --> 1:15:22.822
It's not crap, it's fun.

1:15:22.866 --> 1:15:25.782
And good morning to you,sleepy head.

1:15:26.391 --> 1:15:27.958
[static buzzing]

1:15:30.526 --> 1:15:33.267
- Hey, where is everybody?
- I don't know.

1:15:33.311 --> 1:15:36.575
I haven't seen anybody since
we wrapped filming hours ago.

1:15:36.619 --> 1:15:38.272
Where's Scratch?

1:15:38.316 --> 1:15:40.144
I think he went upstairsto take a shower.

1:15:41.667 --> 1:15:43.060
It's midnight.

1:15:43.103 --> 1:15:45.279
Why did you let me
sleep so long?

1:15:45.323 --> 1:15:47.151
You said you wanted to sleep.

1:15:47.194 --> 1:15:49.327
Yeah, well,
we gotta get going.

1:15:49.370 --> 1:15:51.416
Okay, let's go.

1:15:52.069 --> 1:15:53.723
[sighs]

1:15:56.769 --> 1:15:57.857
Hey.

1:15:57.901 --> 1:15:59.380
[door banging]

1:15:59.424 --> 1:16:01.426
This is stuck.

1:16:01.469 --> 1:16:03.080
You think Vincentlocked us in here?

1:16:03.123 --> 1:16:04.821
Yeah, okay.

1:16:06.083 --> 1:16:07.345
[gasps]

1:16:09.826 --> 1:16:12.393
That can't be the same door
that we just came in.

1:16:12.437 --> 1:16:14.874
Obviously not.

1:16:16.006 --> 1:16:17.616
This house is so weird.

1:16:17.660 --> 1:16:19.487
I don't know, did we
come through this door?

1:16:19.531 --> 1:16:22.229
Freaking creepy.

1:16:22.273 --> 1:16:25.276
I coulda sworn
we came through this door.

1:16:26.190 --> 1:16:27.365
[knob clicks]

1:16:27.408 --> 1:16:29.759
Oh, come on right now!

1:16:29.802 --> 1:16:33.110
- [banging]
- Christina, just open it!

1:16:37.854 --> 1:16:39.507
Come on!

1:16:40.378 --> 1:16:41.945
[gasps]

1:16:41.988 --> 1:16:43.381
What the fuck?

1:16:43.424 --> 1:16:46.079
Language, but you're right.

1:16:46.123 --> 1:16:47.951
What the fuck?

1:16:51.694 --> 1:16:53.043
Oh, God.

1:16:55.698 --> 1:16:59.615
Grab your phone and let's
get the hell out of here.

1:16:59.658 --> 1:17:00.964
Now.

1:17:05.098 --> 1:17:06.752
This is so weird.

1:17:06.796 --> 1:17:08.101
Let's go.

1:17:11.235 --> 1:17:12.976
Shh, shh, shh.

1:17:14.107 --> 1:17:15.456
Okay.

1:17:19.417 --> 1:17:21.114
- Shh, shh.
- I'm scared.

1:17:21.158 --> 1:17:25.336
Listen, baby,
something is not right here.

1:17:25.379 --> 1:17:27.164
You understand me?

1:17:29.166 --> 1:17:32.604
[Vincent] There the bastard willlead me to the office and Tony.

1:17:34.650 --> 1:17:36.608
- I need you to hide in there.
- No.

1:17:36.652 --> 1:17:38.044
- Yeah.
- No.

1:17:38.088 --> 1:17:40.830
Shh, shh, shh, shh, shh.

1:17:40.873 --> 1:17:42.745
I will not let
anything happen to you.

1:17:42.788 --> 1:17:44.224
You understand me?

1:17:46.096 --> 1:17:47.706
You're gonna have to
hide in there.

1:17:47.750 --> 1:17:49.360
No, no, no, no, no.

1:17:49.403 --> 1:17:51.144
- It's gonna be okay, baby.
- Why?

1:17:52.145 --> 1:17:53.756
- You go in there.
- No...

1:17:53.799 --> 1:17:56.497
Please. Please, Nancy, go.

1:18:11.730 --> 1:18:14.080
Thank you for taking care of us.

1:18:14.124 --> 1:18:16.039
That's what we do.

1:18:16.082 --> 1:18:20.086
I've never been to
a funeral parlor
that's open 24 hours.

1:18:20.130 --> 1:18:24.221
It's odd hours for some,
convenient for others.

1:18:25.135 --> 1:18:26.571
We are the only funeral parlor

1:18:26.614 --> 1:18:28.573
open 24 hours
in the neighborhood,

1:18:28.616 --> 1:18:30.270
in fact, the entire region.

1:18:30.314 --> 1:18:32.490
Mm. I guess business is good.

1:18:32.533 --> 1:18:34.797
We provide value.

1:18:34.840 --> 1:18:38.017
As you can see,
there is a casket
for all types of budgets.

1:18:38.061 --> 1:18:41.281
Usually they select one
based on who the person was

1:18:41.325 --> 1:18:42.761
during the course of their life.

1:18:42.805 --> 1:18:44.632
What type of person
was your father, Richard?

1:18:44.676 --> 1:18:46.547
[Richard] A real piece of work.

1:18:46.591 --> 1:18:48.506
But it's her father.

1:18:48.549 --> 1:18:51.639
Yes, unfortunately he was.

1:18:51.683 --> 1:18:54.686
Look, I just wanna bury the manand move on with my life, okay?

1:18:54.730 --> 1:18:56.557
The man wasn't present
throughout my whole life,

1:18:56.601 --> 1:18:59.169
and he treated my mother
like shit till her death.

1:18:59.212 --> 1:19:00.474
So, it's his turn.

1:19:00.518 --> 1:19:03.260
So, you know what just,
whatever.

1:19:03.303 --> 1:19:05.088
Very sorry to hear that.

1:19:06.002 --> 1:19:07.655
I understand.

1:19:07.699 --> 1:19:09.179
If it's price, we have options.

1:19:09.222 --> 1:19:12.095
No, he left us a ton of money,

1:19:12.138 --> 1:19:14.793
as well as a ton of money
to bury him.

1:19:17.056 --> 1:19:20.233
That one.
Let's just go with that one.

1:19:20.277 --> 1:19:22.496
Four-two-two-nine-eight.

1:19:22.540 --> 1:19:24.455
For the price,
you can't beat it.

1:19:24.498 --> 1:19:26.457
[laughing]

1:19:29.068 --> 1:19:33.420
So how long will we be
laying Fred out for viewing?

1:19:33.464 --> 1:19:36.815
He had no friends or family,
just us.

1:19:36.859 --> 1:19:38.817
I think we can skip that part.

1:19:38.861 --> 1:19:40.993
How much do we save?

1:19:41.037 --> 1:19:43.300
Oh, there will be savings.

1:19:43.343 --> 1:19:45.302
Let's go back to the office.

1:19:45.737 --> 1:19:47.043
Please.

1:19:56.966 --> 1:19:57.923
[beeps]

1:19:57.967 --> 1:20:01.318
Randolph, 4-2-2-9-8, please.

1:20:07.411 --> 1:20:09.543
Christina, please.
[crying]

1:20:15.332 --> 1:20:16.855
Nancy.

1:20:16.899 --> 1:20:19.031
Nancy.

1:20:19.075 --> 1:20:20.685
[whimpering]

1:20:29.607 --> 1:20:31.348
[whimpering]

1:20:36.744 --> 1:20:38.398
[whimpering]

1:20:57.026 --> 1:20:58.984
[panting]

1:21:12.345 --> 1:21:14.260
[Carol] What do you wanna do?
We have, like, five minutes.

1:21:14.304 --> 1:21:16.872
- We gotta check these rooms.
- Fuck.

1:21:30.494 --> 1:21:32.191
It's locked.

1:21:37.762 --> 1:21:39.982
[lock rattling]

1:21:45.639 --> 1:21:46.727
Hey!

1:21:49.643 --> 1:21:52.037
[screaming]

1:21:52.081 --> 1:21:53.865
[grunting]

1:22:09.489 --> 1:22:12.057
[Vincent laughing echoes]

1:22:29.814 --> 1:22:33.122
[Vincent VO] I only wanted
to tell my story, Christina.

1:22:34.862 --> 1:22:36.864
[whimpering]

1:22:41.913 --> 1:22:43.828
[grunting]

1:23:05.806 --> 1:23:06.894
[grunts]

1:23:28.742 --> 1:23:31.528
[grunting]

1:24:16.573 --> 1:24:21.273
[Vincent VO]
You send investigators
into my house to snoop?

1:24:21.317 --> 1:24:24.711
If they had gotten out,
if they had exploited me,

1:24:24.755 --> 1:24:28.324
I would be the first stop on every future investigation.

1:24:28.367 --> 1:24:30.326
I couldn't take that risk,
Christina.

1:24:30.369 --> 1:24:32.415
- So it ends tonight!
- [screams]

1:24:32.458 --> 1:24:34.504
[crying]

1:24:36.506 --> 1:24:37.855
[grunts]

1:24:37.898 --> 1:24:39.857
[screams]

1:24:40.684 --> 1:24:43.034
[whimpering]

1:24:43.078 --> 1:24:45.080
[Vincent grunts]

1:24:50.259 --> 1:24:52.391
That's right, it does.

1:24:53.088 --> 1:24:55.090
[screams]

1:24:57.179 --> 1:24:59.920
[panting]

1:25:00.834 --> 1:25:02.140
[whimpers]

1:25:02.184 --> 1:25:05.883
[grunting]

1:25:31.561 --> 1:25:33.606
[muffled gasp]

1:25:36.783 --> 1:25:38.350
Oh, come on.

1:25:39.177 --> 1:25:41.223
No, no, no.

1:25:44.008 --> 1:25:45.401
[grunts]

1:25:48.926 --> 1:25:50.449
Help me.

1:25:53.017 --> 1:25:56.107
- No, no, no, no, no.
- [Randolph grunting]

1:25:56.151 --> 1:25:57.848
[grunts]

